lead_paragraph: The rare execution of a prince rocketed around social media, with some Saudis saying they never imagined such a thing would happen and others saying it showed the quality of their justice system.

headline.print_headline: Saudi Prince Is Executed for Murder
headline.main: Saudi Arabia Executes a Prince Convicted in a Fatal Shooting

snippet: The rare execution of a prince rocketed around social media, with some Saudis saying they never imagined such a thing would happen and others saying it showed the quality of their justice system....
abstract: Saudi Arabia executes Prince Turki bin Saud bin Turki bin Saud al-Kabeer after he is convicted of fatally shooting man in brawl; incident marks first time kingdom has subjected member of royalty to capital punishment in four decades.
